trans-unit.source: Dynamically manufactures Web service handler instances, whose type or types implement the <xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"></xref> interface.
trans-unit.target: Dinamicamente fabrica instâncias do manipulador de serviço da Web, cujo tipo ou tipos de implementam o <xref href="System.Web.IHttpHandler"> </xref> interface.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface establishes the contract that ASP.NET uses to process incoming HTTP Web requests with custom HTTP handlers.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>interface estabelece o contrato que o ASP.NET usa para processar solicitações HTTP da Web com manipuladores HTTP personalizados de entrada.</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>

trans-unit.source: The WebServiceHandlerFactory class produces an instance of an <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> implementation for handling Web service requests.
trans-unit.target: A classe WebServiceHandlerFactory produz uma instância de um <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>implementação para lidar com solicitações de serviço Web.</xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.WebServiceHandlerFactory"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.WebServiceHandlerFactory"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"></xref> that provides references to intrinsic server objects (For example, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Request*>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Response*>, <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Session*>, and <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.Server*>) used to service HTTP requests.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.Web.HttpContext"> </xref> que fornece referências a objetos do servidor intrínsecos (por exemplo, <> </> *>, <> </> *>, <> </> *>, e <> </> *>) usado para atender solicitações HTTP.

trans-unit.source: The HTTP data transfer method (GET or POST) that the client uses.
trans-unit.target: Método (GET ou POST) que usa o cliente de transferência de dados HTTP.

trans-unit.source: The raw URL of the requested resource.
trans-unit.target: A URL bruta do recurso solicitado.

trans-unit.source: The file-system path of the requested resource.
trans-unit.target: O caminho do sistema de arquivos do recurso solicitado.

trans-unit.source: There are no resources associated with a handler instance that the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.WebServiceHandlerFactory> class needs to release.
trans-unit.target: Não há nenhum recurso associado a um manipulador de instância que o <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.WebServiceHandlerFactory>a classe precisa liberar.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.WebServiceHandlerFactory>
